data.description: Lovely country estate with front porch, second floor balcony, two car garage screened in patio level back fence yard leads to trail to the golf course. Hardwood floors on the first floor family room with fireplace. Great room with fireplace. Tiled sunroom or children’s retreat that leads to covered screened patio. This home has a separate dining room and eat in kitchen, white cabinets with granite countertops, wall oven and slide in stainless steel stove. Updated hall bath too. This homes layout is made for relaxing and social gatherings. Upstairs boast, four bedrooms, and two full baths. The owners suite bath has updated vanities and countertops, tile floors and walk-in shower. Three additional spacious bedrooms are newly plush carpeted. hall bath has tub/shower combo. The great room is the length of the house. This is a beautiful versatile room. Next to this room is the tiled bonus room that can be used as a children’s retreat, game room or Sunroom. This room can be exited to the backyard, or it can exit to the screened in patio. The screened in patio exits to the level, fenced backyard and if the pool is desired, this backyard might be able to fit a pool. Walking virtual tours for buyers by request. Home is available for sale and for lease purchase with the option paid upfront and seller will consider their one year or two years on the lease part.
